{"type": "article", "id": 7629, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-03-23T08:45:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2263, "name": "台灯"}, {"id": 8060, "name": "减震车轮"}, {"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 266, "name": "椅子"}, {"id": 2284, "name": "桌子"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607143230KnQAtgIYDay2zETM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tConductive Knot Lamp by Celia Torvisco\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tCelia Torvisco 推出的这一款灯有一个非常巧妙的开关，两根绳子分别是两根导电线，只要把绳子两端系在一起就可以点亮电灯，而当结解开便可以关掉电灯。系在一起的绳子也可以挂在各种不同需要的地方，美观和实用兼备。这款灯有白色、黑色、蓝黑等颜色可选，不过目前还没开卖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143214a5TIkYcp2BMVbuF0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85452323\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143215ckDR7u8geBCIyWTa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143215a62ULuqtEXnfpJYD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143216vaxGYuygMqsJIRKn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143216nVuafOyR58s1dWhM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071432162RpX4fJAYzbiOvwe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67603912\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tLoopwheel by Sam Pearce\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t英国发明家 Sam Pearce 设计了一种名为 Loopwheel 的减震车轮，他用轮轴与轮圈之间的弹簧片取代了传统的辐条，车轮采用碳纤维材料，大大减轻了车轮在崎岖不平的道路上行驶时容易受到的震动。Pearce 从婴儿车获得灵感，并用了四年多的时间来反复修改，车轮既可以用于普通的自行车，也可以用在轮椅上。去年这项设计获得了<a href=\"http://www.designsoftheyear.com/\" target=\"_blank\">“年度设计大奖”</a>，被认为革新了车轮的结构。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143217MUNcYjiuRPVhEqx5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143217cNq0BVy9X7g6SiAj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143218knSKGCo2v1TUPlwq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40393013\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071432181Zbm2947gMicPJXH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143219ruSyqAijB0R9a1QU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143219xrofPI8zuaZ0S3NE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61400651\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tMini-kitchen &amp; Smart table by NáBITO\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tNáBITO 设计公司推出的这两款小推车实际上分别是一个多功能智能学习桌和一个多功能智能小厨房。小推车外形看起来是一个线条流畅的长方体，但内部伸展开来却别有洞天。智能桌子除了普通的桌面设施，还包含有蓝牙音箱、电线、小冰箱和储物柜；而小厨房有切菜板、冰箱、灶台和微波炉，并且配有大小不同的抽屉和储物柜，基本上可以满足小规模的烹饪需求。不过<a href=\"http://nabitoarchitects.com/\" target=\"_blank\">他们的网站</a>最近在维护中，所以我们可能需要过段时间才能看到购买信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143220tWgaLD0RGmx6I8U7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65892421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143220LerROp40K2Q9Buil.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143220esfz8Bd7QbuRO6MX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63814181\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143221LuMcxYr3DgsOpHCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70293399\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143221Y4i7RPEZ16FV0IgA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143222yM0GiljRAghI7keq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tLinito by Yu Ito\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t春天来了，一切都变得五彩缤纷起来。日本设计师 Yu ito 给意大利家居品牌设计了一套叫做 Linito 的系列家具，折叠的风格本身具有日本传统文化“折纸”的要素，而钢片是现代化的产物，再加上活泼靓丽的色彩，整套家具看上去舒适又愉快。<a href=\"https://www.formabilio.com/shop/design-chairs/chairs/contemporary-chair-linito\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>，感兴趣的话你可以点进来看看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143222GunegTf7jM9BQXJw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143223NUFZpvst0jKYQwEq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143223WN2jQAKs6nmtXyfg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143224zC4bLiRyhAcFPsBo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143224MVzaFH6G7K5kCnAP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143224sPBGDet798HMT5pE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071432255qVoAsmdD9zJkn3v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tDita by Désormeaux/carrette &amp; Metylos\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t法国工作室 Désormeaux/carrette 和 Metylos 共同完成的这款小灯名字叫做 Dita，简单的木制底座上嵌入了灯泡，而有趣的是，他们给普通的灯泡加上了一层外衣，是一个毛毡材质的灯罩，这个像连衣裙一样的小灯罩让台灯一下子变得时尚动感了起来，而从木制平面灯具到灯罩的环绕，也展现了从二维转变到三维的时尚进程。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143225KRcFYhBAUwLV690H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143226CTUmJK49EZyQ5xr3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143226xYnZCzPgQpTeqyWA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060714322737lUEH9hLZzdSkpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143227TL9dXbeEHoqZ7kAp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143228Qbv8PCB2i3dN7zaH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071432296YlMmE0H47Ud9h2x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71760391\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143229m4W60zoYROUQ3GTX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41442543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}